# Nimbus Component Patterns

## Layout: Docs Layout (default for this project)

```html
// Sidebar: w-[240px], sticky, left
// Content: max-w-[760px], px-nimbus-8
// TOC (optional): w-[200px], right, sticky

<div class="flex min-h-screen bg-nimbus-surface">
  <aside class="w-[240px] shrink-0 sticky top-0 h-screen border-r border-nimbus-border bg-nimbus-surface-subtle"></aside>
  <main class="flex-1 max-w-[760px] px-nimbus-8 py-nimbus-6"></main>
  <nav class="w-[200px] shrink-0 sticky top-0 h-screen"></nav> <!-- optional TOC -->
</div>
```

Top bar height: `h-[56px]`. Sidebar width: `w-[240px]`.

## Buttons

```html
// Primary
<button class="min-w-[96px] h-[36px] px-nimbus-4 rounded-nimbus-md
  bg-nimbus-primary text-white font-medium text-[14px]
  hover:bg-nimbus-primary-hover active:bg-nimbus-primary-active
  focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-nimbus-primary focus-visible:ring-offset-2
  disabled:opacity-40 disabled:pointer-events-none
  transition-[background-color,box-shadow] duration-[120ms] ease-out">
  Label
</button>

// Secondary (Ghost)
<button class="min-w-[96px] h-[36px] px-nimbus-4 rounded-nimbus-md
  border border-nimbus-border text-nimbus-text-primary
  hover:bg-nimbus-surface-subtle
  focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-nimbus-primary focus-visible:ring-offset-2
  disabled:opacity-40 disabled:pointer-events-none">
  Label
</button>

// Destructive
<button class="... bg-nimbus-error text-white hover:opacity-90">Delete</button>
```

## Cards

```html
// Default
<div class="rounded-nimbus-lg border border-nimbus-border bg-nimbus-surface shadow-nimbus-sm p-nimbus-4">

// Elevated
<div class="rounded-nimbus-lg bg-nimbus-surface shadow-nimbus-md p-nimbus-6">
```

Card title spacing: `mb-nimbus-3`. Body text: `text-nimbus-text-secondary`.

## Alerts

```html
// success | warning | error | info
<div class="flex gap-nimbus-2 rounded-nimbus-md border p-nimbus-3 border-nimbus-info text-nimbus-info" role="alert">
  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">info</span>
  <div>
    <p class="font-medium">Title</p>
    <p class="text-[14px] mt-nimbus-1">Description</p>
  </div>
</div>
```

## Focus & Interaction States

Always include focus-visible ring. Never remove outlines without replacement.

```html
// Focus ring pattern (apply to all interactive elements)
"focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-nimbus-primary focus-visible:ring-offset-2"

// Disabled pattern
"disabled:opacity-40 disabled:pointer-events-none"

// Hover/Active for surfaces
"hover:bg-nimbus-surface-subtle active:bg-nimbus-border"
```

## Icons (Material Symbols)

Use the Outlined style. Load via Google Fonts in `fonts.css`:

```html
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined" rel="stylesheet" />
```

```html
// Sizes: 16px (sm), 20px (default), 24px (lg), 32px (hero)
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px] text-nimbus-text-secondary">search</span>

// Icon + label: gap-nimbus-2
<button class="flex items-center gap-nimbus-2" type="button">
  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">add</span>
  New item
</button>

// Icon-only button: 36×36 container
<button class="w-[36px] h-[36px] flex items-center justify-center rounded-nimbus-md" type="button" aria-label="More actions">
  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">more_vert</span>
</button>
```

Do not mix Outlined and Rounded/Sharp styles in the same view.

## Motion

```tsx
// Page transitions: fade + slide 8px, motion-medium
"transition-[opacity,transform] duration-[180ms] ease-[ease]"

// Component transitions: motion-fast
"transition-[background-color,box-shadow] duration-[120ms] ease-out"

// Chip press: scale-[0.98]
// Dropdown: translate-y-2 + opacity-0 → translate-y-0 + opacity-100
```

## Accessibility Checklist (WCAG 2.2 AA)

- Text contrast ≥ 4.5:1 (`text-nimbus-text-primary` on `bg-nimbus-surface` is compliant)
- Interactive elements contrast ≥ 3:1
- All interactive elements keyboard-focusable with visible focus ring
- Icon-only buttons have `aria-label`
- Form inputs have associated `<label>` or `aria-label`
